{"id": "ChIJFeT8Ry_GwoARKyTECxHrGJ4", "rating": 3.6, "userRatingCount": 275, "displayName": {"text": "Bodega", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJFeT8Ry_GwoARKyTECxHrGJ4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSellqWm9UazR3YzFGRlFXSmhXbWRhUVU5dmFXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "I placed an order on March 8 and have not received any shipping update or response from customer support.\n\nI tried contacting Bodega by email and also left a comment asking about my order, but so far there has been no reply.\n\nAt this point I no longer even want the item, I just wanted a response or some transparency about the order status.\n\nBecause of the complete lack of communication, I had to open a chargeback with bank.\n\nVery disappointing experience for a store that is supposed to be reputable.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I placed an order on March 8 and have not received any shipping update or response from customer support.\n\nI tried contacting Bodega by email and also left a comment asking about my order, but so far there has been no reply.\n\nAt this point I no longer even want the item, I just wanted a response or some transparency about the order status.\n\nBecause of the complete lack of communication, I had to open a chargeback with bank.\n\nVery disappointing experience for a store that is supposed to be reputable.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Max Champion", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105110397231422529792/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDBP87m3hhNV7QguQy_JIGeTLJjc4Cl1v-dJomJBfTNVsSKIg8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-14T23:50:39.711643745Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSellqWm9UazR3YzFGRlFXSmhXbWRhUVU5dmFXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSellqWm9UazR3YzFGRlFXSmhXbWRhUVU5dmFXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c62f47fce415:0x9e18eb110bc4242b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFeT8Ry_GwoARKyTECxHrGJ4/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNfOE1EZG1nRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "Cool selection of items but the staff there are too cool to acknowledge any customers walking in, or at all really. They really don't bother looking up. At a store front that spends so much effort on aesthetics, maybe focus on customer service. The \"too cool for school\" aesthetic in LA is outplayed and embarrassing really 😂", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Cool selection of items but the staff there are too cool to acknowledge any customers walking in, or at all really. They really don't bother looking up. At a store front that spends so much effort on aesthetics, maybe focus on customer service. The \"too cool for school\" aesthetic in LA is outplayed and embarrassing really 😂", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Robert Lucero", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111663104726616922472/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnfT9oQY4BAxsIF5eWVALHPDhZ5yvAeVt9DdBrm9GHJ1bpk3ED=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-01-16T10:50:28.575220Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNfOE1EZG1nRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNfOE1EZG1nRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c62f47fce415:0x9e18eb110bc4242b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFeT8Ry_GwoARKyTECxHrGJ4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3NVVqUllVSEJ4ZEZodVVtNVlMVko2V2xWTU1WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing atmosphere super hidden iykyk but once you find it you’d be amazed. Also cool free photo booth.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing atmosphere super hidden iykyk but once you find it you’d be amazed. Also cool free photo booth.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Benny Giang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103361947473804426175/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1HQIeaoAO0fUKYOIwOO7ENjn2WAMqPZOOECCcSlt1E_Bdh8WE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-25T01:04:52.280890090Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3NVVqUllVSEJ4ZEZodVVtNVlMVko2V2xWTU1WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3NVVqUllVSEJ4ZEZodVVtNVlMVko2V2xWTU1WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c62f47fce415:0x9e18eb110bc4242b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJFeT8Ry_GwoARKyTECxHrGJ4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xrM1dFdERTR1Z0Tm5Kd2JYZzJlbTV5TlRndFVWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Customer service in this place nosedived, use to be a cool spot now the employees think they are too cool and hardly look up and they won’t give a refund even if something is unworn with tags so they might as well say all sales are final… idk what happened to this place but I’m definitely not coming back after years shopping here", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Customer service in this place nosedived, use to be a cool spot now the employees think they are too cool and hardly look up and they won’t give a refund even if something is unworn with tags so they might as well say all sales are final… idk what happened to this place but I’m definitely not coming back after years shopping here", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "K G", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117013618389540871481/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6x1eScYH0_kPsnb16riBYwWg-wJsVwc7sHAo_i8gHCUQR9Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publ